title: Researchers Develop New Technique to Wipe Dangerous Knowledge From AI Systems
description: Researchers have developed new techniques to prevent AI models from being used to carry out cyberattacks and deploy bioweapons.

title: OpenAI Says Musk Agreed the ChatGPT Maker Should Become a For-Profit Company
description: Elon Musk supported making OpenAI a for-profit company, the ChatGPT maker said, attacking a lawsuit from the wealthy investor.
